{"title":"安装指南","markdown":{"headingText":"安装指南","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## 系统要求\n\n### 必需组件\n\n1. **Stata 17 或更高版本** - 必须已安装在您的计算机上\n2. **VS Code / Cursor / Antigravity** - 任一支持的 IDE\n3. **UV 包管理器** - 扩展会自动安装，也可手动安装\n\n### 推荐配置\n\n- **Python 3.11+**（Windows 上必需）\n- **内存**：每个 Stata 会话需要约 200-300 MB RAM\n\n## VS Code 安装\n\n### 选项 1：从 VS Code 市场安装（推荐）\n\n```bash\ncode --install-extension DeepEcon.stata-mcp\n```\n\n### 选项 2：从 .vsix 文件安装\n\n1. 从 [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/hanlulong/stata-mcp/releases) 下载 `stata-mcp-0.5.2.vsix`\n2. 安装：\n\n```bash\ncode --install-extension path/to/stata-mcp-0.5.2.vsix\n```\n\n## Cursor 安装\n\n```bash\ncursor --install-extension path/to/stata-mcp-0.5.2.vsix\n```\n\n## Antigravity 安装\n\n1. 打开 Antigravity\n2. 按 `Cmd+Shift+X` 打开扩展视图\n3. 搜索 \"Stata MCP\"\n4. 点击\"安装\"\n\n::: callout-note\n首次安装需要设置依赖项，可能需要最多 **2 分钟**完成。\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":false,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":true,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":false,"code-overflow":"wrap","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"la